
Simple Kustom Html Media Player 

overview : what we're gonna do

Create a folder on the desktop
create a basic blank file inside said folder
edit blank file 
add the basic <html><body> tags
open <audio> tags
open <audio controls> to enable controls
edit code for media files
add <source src = "medianame.extension" type="audio/extension>"
close </audio>
save as KA.html and set encoding to utf8
store the media files in the root folder for easy access.
Run for fun

